// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0023 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 30c29a8f-3ca8-5432-b7e1-9468c0a1bc2d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*alpine:3.22*" or process.executable like~ "*alpine:3.23*" or process.executable like~ "*alpine edge:*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:4.0*")
